        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nlink to processor-db properties: \n\nhttps://github.com/onap/ccsdk-cds/blob/4786e0b9ef3b4b82f4ad14bcffafa222628011d6/ms/blueprintsprocessor/application/src/main/resources/application.properties#L50-L54",
